<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV92">
<l>pēṇala millā varakkarmun nīra perumpativāy</l>
<l>nīṇakar nīḷeri vaittaru ḷāyeṉṟu niṉṉaiviṇṇōr</l>
<l>tāṇilan tōyntu toḻuvarniṉ mūrttipaṟ kūṟṟiloṉṟu</l>
<l>kāṇalu māṅkoleṉ ṟēvaikal mālaiyuṅ kālaiyumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“You who had the grace to put long fire to the long city, to the great ocean abode</l>
<l>of the Rakṣasa who is without estimable goodness”, thus the celestials worship you,</l>
<l>touching the ground at [your] feet – thinking “will there also be seeing your form</l>
<l>as one in many utterances?”, daily [both] evening and morning?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
